OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fbut some low cloud possible in the
OL,9,Feast and Central Belt.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny low cloud in Central
OL,12,FBelt dispersing through the morning to
OL,13,Fleave a dry day with some unbroken
OL,14,Fsunshine. Very warm or hot.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,17,Ffew days with variable amounts of
OL,18,Fcloud and some sunny spells. Gradually
OL,19,Fbecoming less warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
